Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:36.63,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢は風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:44.62,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}光導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢境如風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}指引著光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.27,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}空と雲を…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}將青空和白雲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼沒有食慾？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有不愛吃的東西呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好吃飯的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管吃什麼  反正也治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打點滴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣的話  本來能治好的也治不好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確的說  應該是「治不好的就是治不好」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為本來就是真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢  也要看如何看待這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相當喜歡這個狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很有一種文學性的美感嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種食物玷污自己的身體  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅能品嚐一次的  名為「死」的甘美果實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這誘惑總浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼美好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關上窗戶的話  天使就沒辦法進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  她會來迎接已經清淨身體了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:01.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(註：{\fnふみゴシック\fe128}體を清めた{\r}，為了祭祀等法事而清潔身體)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毫無污瑕的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子又不吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在看著窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是在看那個教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那個不是給人感覺很恐怖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要拆掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  是不是在那裡面能看到了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種話啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會來迎接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  來的應該是死神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把我帶走吧  去那虛無的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來迎接我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  帶我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數值有點高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好靜養可是不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  飯也好好吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一會兒再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了  天使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我不是什麼「天使」了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  你叫作「水銀燈」對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在我眼裡  你就是一位天使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來奪走我生命的  黑色天使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行和我訂下契約的媒介居然是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還快要死掉了  一點力量都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃蘋果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著說剛才的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「愛麗絲遊戲」開始之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會用我的生命來和真紅戰鬥對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一樣可以輕鬆解決掉真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我也就不需要什麼媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣用盡我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這心臟停止跳動吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很遺憾  我不一定能實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次遇到真紅  距離現在已是58萬小時之前的事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在同一時代甦醒的事並不經常發生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我甦醒了  如果還有別人在沉睡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲遊戲就不會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  別抱太大希望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無聊的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？這個感覺是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡戰鬥過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是586920小時前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡和真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:12:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女的第七人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是個愛耍小聰明的妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這力量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵…很強…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  在那個時候變成了廢物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經變成過廢物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  輸給了真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能修好薔薇少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了完成愛麗絲遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時後  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…父親大人…把我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用了我的生命吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一下子就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指變的很熱  心臟像在灼燒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然因為醫生做了多餘的事  讓我沒能死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是已經瀕死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用了你那麼一點點力量就變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始的時候  大家都說我活不過5歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他們就說只能活到7歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後說是10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間裡  大家都很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論再怎麼延長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「馬上就會死」這一點也是不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得還是快點死掉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我的「這裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  我並不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個壞掉的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就是廢物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像天使你一樣完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要成為愛麗絲的完美人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又出現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我不會再被迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不在了  快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚了嗎？真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點小傷害就想把我打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨磨蹭蹭的  我就把你拆成…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是水銀燈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的！我是最適合成為愛麗絲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以父親大人才讓我復活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  已經夠了  今天就只打個招呼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  下次再見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會把你變成廢物的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成永遠不可能修好的廢物碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有句話  一直想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經把你稱作「廢物」  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到純把迷失的布偶和我的手臂喚回的時候  我才明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能注意到那呼喚著自己的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會變成廢物的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有誰從一開始就是廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是哪位姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都擁有與愛麗絲相配的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:25.00,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幸せと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:32.99,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}嫌な思い出…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幸福和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}悲傷的回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續…唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我唱也是沒有意義的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我…只是個廢物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  「愛麗絲遊戲」是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物什麼的  是不應該輕易說出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:14.24,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}優しい今が遠ざかる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今溫柔地遠離而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:20.17,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}靜かな夜  續け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惟有寂靜的夜在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:28.15,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}瞬の內に迂めて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}在一瞬間充滿心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:36.31,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}すがる氣持ち捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}捨棄依賴的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:44.27,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)}全て思い繫げ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)}將所有思念緊緊相連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:22:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  她怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情  都如計劃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純？純？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊  一大早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你給我泡一杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給你自己來一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  打掃一下房間如何？
